# Exchange System

Exchange System is a web application for currency conversion and transactions.

## Features

- Currency Conversion
- User Registration and Login
- Balance Management
- Transaction History
- Real-time Notifications for Transfers

## Technologies Used

- Flask
- Flask-SocketIO
- Flask-Login
- Flask-Migrate
- Flask-WTF
- python-dotenv
- SQLAlchemy
- Zeep

## Getting Started

1. Clone the repository:

   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/your-username/exchange-system.git
###### Install dependencies
   pip install -r requirements.txt
   ###### initalize the database 
   flask db init
   flask db migrate -m "initial migration"
   flask db upgrade
   ###### Run the application
   python run.py
   ###### Open the application in your browser:
   http://127.0.0.1:5000/


